    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到 Extinct VR 的世界，这是一款身临其境的单人动作冒险和探索 VR 体验，它将带您进入一个充满奇异事件和挑战性障碍的奇异世界。在 Extinct VR 中，你将扮演一个被推入非凡环境的普通人，在一个迷人的宇宙中穿梭，每个角落都隐藏着新的奥秘。                                    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179710/extras/9b06d5658024e9dc23d8421fe91d8e56.poster.avif?t=1739206964\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179710/extras/9b06d5658024e9dc23d8421fe91d8e56.webm?t=1739206964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179710/extras/9b06d5658024e9dc23d8421fe91d8e56.mp4?t=1739206964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这里，你会遇到各种独特的生命形式，让人联想到一个面临灭亡的先进文明的半机械人残余。当你深入这个神秘的世界时，你将面临一系列谜题和强大的敌人，每个敌人都有自己的战术和弱点。                </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179710/extras/fa58ebdff6f67e5fedda41403803e358.poster.avif?t=1739206964\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179710/extras/fa58ebdff6f67e5fedda41403803e358.webm?t=1739206964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179710/extras/fa58ebdff6f67e5fedda41403803e358.mp4?t=1739206964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179710/extras/d632596582d90a9254e92fa0765c57b7.poster.avif?t=1739206964\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179710/extras/d632596582d90a9254e92fa0765c57b7.webm?t=1739206964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179710/extras/d632596582d90a9254e92fa0765c57b7.mp4?t=1739206964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过自由移动和传送机制体验自由移动，您可以探索周围环境，并以前所未有的方式与环境互动。Extinct VR 还有一个带坐姿游戏功能的模式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179710/extras/86de235e6cd0689b14f5ec935ba3524b.poster.avif?t=1739206964\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179710/extras/86de235e6cd0689b14f5ec935ba3524b.webm?t=1739206964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179710/extras/86de235e6cd0689b14f5ec935ba3524b.mp4?t=1739206964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入我们这段惊险刺激的旅程吧，勇气、智慧和机智是您最大的盟友。你能揭开 Extinct VR 的秘密，并在重重考验中幸存下来吗？</p>",
